{"type": "article", "id": 18664, "title": "放铅笔的桌面工具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-08T07:41:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125723uVd8g4p7UN6M5iAs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是墨尔本的设计工作室 Dowel Jones 带来的固定铅笔的桌面工具，是用橡木制作的，近似正方形，上面有几道放铅笔的波浪纹凹槽，也可以放上橡皮擦，很清新自然，也是一个小的装饰物件。有黑色、白色和自然色三种，可以将颜色错开拼在一起开发出更多用途。<a href=\"http://doweljones.com/products/blocchi?variant=1155168465\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125721QzMUe6fukRgjxDEy.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125721vIhBSjbAGs7UWDZa.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125722F2dyEGe3YoLPtkNm.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125722ofPOVj84F6ehisK3.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257230eUlIx2AT5ZoS1gV.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}